Whiteout Detection¶

Whitewashed / Hidden information from documents.¶

Who¶

  • Ammar Alhashmi.

Contents¶

  1. Types & Examples of whitewashed content.
  2. Proposed solutions
  3. Results.

Types & Examples of whitewashed content¶

  • Personal information such as names and segnature.
  • Informative statements.
  • Covered with either colored blocks or figures such as squares or triangles

Personal Information¶

  • names and signature.

Informative statements¶

  • Informative text or paragraphs

Proposed Ideas / Solutions¶

  • Whitewashed detection based on colour, shape and edges.
  • Another possibility is introducing NLP.

Results¶

A json file that contains the following:

  • Detected whitewashed text with their coordinates
  • Type of whitewashed text (personal info or statements)
  • Estimation of the number of whitewashed words.
